<% web_url = Rails.application.config_for(:app).web_url! -%>
Dear submitter,

A DDBJ curator (<%= @curator.uid %>) has posted a message on your <%= @submission.db.humanize %> submission (<%= @submission.source_id.presence || "##{@submission.id}" %>):

  <%= @message.body.lines.map { "  #{it}" }.join.chomp %>

Open the thread on the web UI to reply:
<%= File.join(web_url, @submission.db, 'submissions', @submission.id.to_s) %>

Regards,
DDBJ Repository
